description: Whenever I think that nothing can shock me anymore a new client proves the opposite. Today another young man called me to visit him and explain him how I could help him. Of course they always think that I am granting loads. When I came there I found a desperate guy in an almost empty apartment which is obviously undergoing some basic, cheap reconstruction. All his private belongings have been put together in a box and apart from that there was just a mattress. His debts were enormous. Almost 100 000 CZK. Usually I do not offer more than 40 000 CZK which is in most cases enough. So I offered him this amount which I had in cash with me and asked him to get naked and have some fun with me in return...
title: Debt Dandy 112
